%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sairat%20Leads%20Reunite%20Online%3A%20Rinku%20Rajguru%20shares%20candid%20Instagram%20pic%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778330429000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-130977602%2Cimgsize-51160.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fmarathi%2Fmovies%2Fnews%2Fnostalgia-alert-rinku-rajguru-akash-thosars-latest-photo-brings-back-sairat-memories%2Farticleshow%2F130977602.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F130977602.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EFans%20are%20buzzing%20with%20excitement%20after%20'Sairat'%20stars%20Rinku%20Rajguru%20and%20Akash%20Thosar%20posted%20a%20playful%20photo%20on%20Instagram.%20The%20pair%2C%20beloved%20for%20their%20captivating%20portrayal%20in%20the%202016%20Marathi%20box%20office%20success%20that%20inspired%20a%20Bollywood%20adaptation%2C%20brought%20back%20fond%20memories%20of%20their%20dynamic%20on-screen%20romance.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sonal%20Khandelwal%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20moved%20back%20in%20with%20my%20parents%20at%2024.%20It%20made%20me%20grow%20up%20way%20more%20than%20renting%20with%20friends.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221121%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20packs%20up%20the%20contents%20of%20her%20apartment%20before%20moving%20back%20in%20with%20her%20parents.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fc8284c9dd4cb81cda8040%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22841%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%2C%20shown%20packing%20up%20her%20apartment%2C%20said%20that%20she%20was%20initially%20embarrassed%20about%20moving%20back%20in%20with%20her%20parents.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Eliza%20Pepper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThere's%20a%20lot%20of%20negative%20discourse%20around%20adult%20children%20moving%20back%20in%20with%20their%20parents.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20made%20the%20move%20last%20year%2C%20after%20my%20mom%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20cancer.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI've%20grown%20up%20more%20over%20the%20past%20few%20months%20living%20at%20home%20than%20I%20did%20while%20renting.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20fall%2C%20I%20felt%20like%20a%20picture%20of%20success%20in%20my%2020s.%20I%20was%20developing%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvaluable-lessons-to-learn-in-your-first-job-2015-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efast-paced%20career%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20living%20in%20central%20London%20with%20friends%2C%20and%20had%20just%20enough%20time%20and%20money%20to%20enjoy%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20the%20life%20I'd%20built%20collapsed.%20In%20quick%20succession%2C%20my%20mum%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20cancer%2C%20and%20my%20grandfather%20suffered%20a%20debilitating%20stroke.%20While%20friends%20continued%20with%20the%20cycle%20of%20work%20and%20socials%2C%20I%20was%20shocked%20into%20pausing%20mine%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboomerang-kids-moving-back-in-with-parents-saving-money-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emove%20back%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20with%20my%20parents%20at%2024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENothing%20could%20make%20me%20trade%20being%20with%20my%20family%20during%20this%20crisis%2C%20so%20why%20did%20I%20feel%20embarrassed%20admitting%20I%20lived%20at%20home%20to%20acquaintances%20or%20colleagues%20who%20didn't%20have%20the%20context%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEverywhere%20I%20looked%2C%20there%20was%20a%20narrative%20that%20adults%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-moved-back-home-several-times-boomerang-child-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elive%20with%20their%20parents%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20regressive%20dependents%2C%20resented%20by%20their%20families.%20That%20certainly%20doesn't%20fit%20my%20situation%2C%20and%20it%20can't%20possibly%20apply%20to%20the%20majority%20of%20Gen%20Zers%2C%20who%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20live%20with%20their%20parents%20than%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcls.ucl.ac.uk%2Fgen-z-more-likely-to-live-with-parents-in-early-20s-than-previous-generations%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eearlier%20generations%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a9e505bd-2855-4e69-b10c-8f81ea445c1e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDefining%20%26quot%3Badulthood%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20felt%20%26quot%3Badult%26quot%3B%20when%20I%20first%20moved%20out%2C%20but%20looking%20back%2C%20it%20was%20permission%20to%20be%20immature.%20The%20logistics%20were%20easy%2C%20I%20could%20do%20whatever%20I%20wanted%2C%20and%20my%20greatest%20commitment%20was%20making%20rent%20each%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222049%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20and%20her%20family%20look%20over%20a%20cliff.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fc852de1443b8dc48e2b72%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221537%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%2C%20who%20recently%20moved%20home%20to%20help%20care%20for%20her%20parents%2C%20says%20she%20enjoys%20getting%20to%20know%20them%20as%20an%20adult.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Eliza%20Pepper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20faced%20a%20family%20crisis%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcaregiving-balance-full-time-job-caring-for-mom-teens-family-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecaregiving%20responsibilities%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20can%20firmly%20say%20I'm%20much%20more%20grown-up%20now.%20Many%20adult%20children%20living%20with%20parents%20will%20have%20learned%20similar%20adult%20lessons%2C%20whether%20they've%20boomeranged%20home%20for%20a%20career%20break%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffollowed-partner-to-new-york-broke-up-went-home-atlanta-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eafter%20a%20breakup%3C%2Fa%3E.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EI%20also%20have%20greater%20responsibilities%20at%20home%20than%20I%20ever%20did%20as%20a%20tenant.%20Though%20I%20initially%20struggled%20with%20the%20shock%20of%20the%20situation%20and%20my%20increased%20commitments%2C%20handling%20challenges%20as%20part%20of%20a%20family%20unit%20is%20probably%20more%20representative%20of%20my%20future%20adult%20life%20which%20will%20likely%20incluvde%20mortgages%2C%20childcare%2C%20and%20any%20other%20curveballs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20circumstances%20are%20rare%2C%20with%20the%20majority%20of%20Gen-Z%20living%20at%20home%20for%20financial%20reasons%20like%20volatile%20income%2C%20unaffordable%20rent%2C%20and%20saving%20to%20get%20on%20the%20property%20ladder.%20Still%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20it's%20right%20that%20my%20peers%20are%20labeled%20as%20childish%20for%20living%20with%20their%20parents%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20more%20mature%20than%20the%20alternative%20of%20debt%20or%20relying%20on%20family%20to%20bail%20you%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20sometimes%20think%20landlords%2C%20perhaps%2C%20are%20the%20main%20group%20benefiting%20from%20the%20belief%20that%20adults%20move%20out%20of%20the%20family%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b2893d0e-9f66-4142-b7d3-db23fb215937%5C%22%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cstrong%3EAging%20goes%20both%20ways%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20what%20I've%20seen%2C%20the%20current%20conversation%20focuses%20only%20on%20the%20right%20age%20for%20children%20to%20move%20out.%20In%20my%20experience%2C%20the%20real%20challenge%20is%20how%20families%20can%20age%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETransitioning%20from%20a%20parent-child%20relationship%20to%20an%20adult-adult%20one%20rewards%20both%20sides.%20Since%20moving%20home%2C%20I've%20gotten%20to%20know%20my%20parents%20more%20deeply.%20I've%20learned%20stories%20of%20their%20past%20and%20worries%20for%20their%20future%20that%20I%20never%20heard%20as%20a%20child%20and%20probably%20wouldn't%20have%20caught%20during%20occasional%20phone%20calls%20or%20holiday%20visits.%20Though%20the%20worst%20circumstances%20brought%20me%20back%20to%20my%20parents%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchange-relationship-with-parents-felt-like-adult-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebuilding%20our%20adult%20relationship%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20a%20silver%20lining.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20though%20headlines%20feature%20parents%20complaining%20their%20retirement%20plans%20are%20ruined%20by%20adult%20children%20moving%20home%2C%20I%20see%20this%20as%20an%20unnecessarily%20negative%20view%20of%20how%20the%20parent-child%20relationship%20evolves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoles%20reverse%20as%20our%20parents%20age.%20Though%20I've%20faced%20this%20earlier%20than%20most%2C%2010%25%20of%20adults%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchange-relationship-with-parents-felt-like-adult-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eproviding%20elder%20care%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20any%20time%2C%20and%20many%20are%20sandwiched%20between%20being%20a%20caring%20child%20and%20caring%20for%20a%20child%20themselves%20%E2%80%94%20it%20doesn't%20sound%20like%20adults%20should%20be%20independent%20to%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20mom%20is%20balancing%20her%20own%20diagnosis%20while%20supporting%20my%20grandparents.%20When%20I%20asked%20her%20if%20becoming%20an%20adult%20meant%20living%20independently%2C%20she%20quipped%2C%20%26quot%3BThey%20say%20it%20takes%20a%20village%2C%20but%20we%20don't%20think%20about%20those%20children%20becoming%20villagers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboomerang-kid-adult-living-with-parents-made-me-grow-up-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778330101000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fc82933cfefc31768d6854%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%2