7236638%3Frefer%3Dembed%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%E2%99%AC%20original%20sound%20-%20Yuqohs%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3C%2Fsection%3E%20%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3ENoah%20Lewis%2C%20a%20high%20schooler%20in%20Delaware%2C%20started%20playing%20about%20two%20weeks%20ago%20with%20his%20friends%20after%20seeing%20some%20baseball%20players%20do%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20now%20every%20morning%20we%20play%2C%20and%20at%20lunch%20we%20play%20in%20the%20gym%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20me.%20He%20and%20his%20friends%20created%20a%20TikTok%20account%2C%20%40scsackers2026%2C%20just%20for%20their%20new%20hobby.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22786f8bbb-e8d8-4fd0-91b7-585f0a61c16d%5C%22%3EThe%20trend%20started%20in%20high%20schools%20a%20few%20weeks%20ago%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it's%20a%20very%20high%20school%20thing%20right%20now%2C%20and%20you'll%20see%20it%20sneak%20into%20the%20mainstream%20in%20a%20month%20or%20so%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Henry%20De%20Tolla%2C%20who%2C%20as%20the%20viral%20account%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40h00pify%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EH00pify%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20on%20TikTok%2C%20is%20kind%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstephen-a-smith-espn-deal-lesson-pay-negotiations-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EStephen%20A.%20Smith%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20youth%20sport%20memes%2C%20cataloging%20trends%20online.%20(He%20was%20one%20of%20the%20earliest%20commentators%20to%20catch%20the%20rise%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsix-seven-forty-one-gen-alpha-slang-meme-brainrot-ai-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20%26quot%3B67%26quot%3B%20meme%3C%2Fa%3E.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20a%20small%20part%20of%20it%20is%20kids%20starting%20to%20want%20to%20get%20off%20social%20media%20and%20do%20stuff%20in%20real%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20De%20Tolla%20said.%20And%20while%20most%20of%20the%20play%20is%20offline%2C%20there's%20also%20an%20irony-tinged%20social%20media%20world%20around%20the%20trend.%20TikTok%20and%20Instagram%20accounts%20have%20popped%20up%20in%20the%20last%20two%20weeks%20for%20school%20%26quot%3Bteams%26quot%3B%20or%20clubs%2C%20and%20kids%20will%20post%20as%20if%20it's%20a%20real%20sport.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20TikTok%20account%20I%20saw%20was%20a%20teenage%20boy%20in%20New%20Jersey%20sharing%20a%20bit%20about%20his%20journey%20to%20make%20his%20school's%20%26quot%3Bvarsity%26quot%3B%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bostonglobe.com%2F2026%2F05%2F07%2Fmetro%2Fhacky-sack%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBoston%20Globe%20reported%20on%20the%20trend%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20something%20blowing%20up%20with%20Massachusetts%20teens%2C%20giving%20an%20example%20of%20an%20Instagram%20account%20%40MIAAhackysack%20that%20pretends%20to%20be%20the%20Massachusetts%20Interscholastic%20Athletic%20Association%2C%20the%20body%20that%20organizes%20the%20state's%20high%20school%20sports%20leagues%20and%20tournaments%2C%20and%20gives%20updated%20rankings%20of%20schools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20the%20trend%20seems%20to%20have%20started%20in%20the%20Northeast%2C%20just%20after%20spring%20break.%20The%20Boston%20Globe%20noted%20that%20recent%20Google%20search%20activity%20for%20the%20term%20was%20concentrated%20in%20Massachusetts%20and%20Connecticut.%20De%20Tolla%20said%20he%20noticed%20it%20in%20the%20videos%2C%20starting%20with%20the%20New%20England%20prep%20school%20lacrosse%20circuit.%20For%20those%20of%20us%20old%20enough%20to%20associate%20hacky%20sacks%20with%20Phish%20fans%20or%20extras%20in%20the%20movie%20%26quot%3BPCU%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Gen%20Z%20version%20might%20be%20a%20little%20different%20%E2%80%94%20it%20seems%20to%20be%20a%20hit%20with%20the%20preppy%20jocks%20rather%20than%20the%20stoner%20burnouts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22480fa29f-eef0-4ada-af20-e08b8d675875%5C%22%3EThe%20Labubu%20effect%3A%20stores%20are%20selling%20out%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENina%20Clarke%2C%20a%20parent%20of%20two%20teens%20at%20a%20private%20school%20in%20Connecticut%2C%20said%20her%20son%2C%20in%20the%2011th%20grade%2C%20and%20all%20his%20friends%20are%20suddenly%20into%20it%2C%20much%20to%20her%20amusement%20as%20a%20Gen%20Xer%20who%20played%20it%20in%20college.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20hitch%20to%20the%20sudden%20popularity%3A%20It's%20hard%20to%20find%20hacky%20sacks%20%E2%80%94%20also%20called%20footbags%20%E2%80%94%20in%20stores%20now.%20Clarke%20said%20she%20went%20to%20Dick's%20Sporting%20Goods%20and%20some%20other%20local%20stores%2C%20but%20they%20had%20all%20been%20completely%20wiped%20out%20of%20stock%20in%20the%20last%20week.%20Finally%2C%20she%20found%20one%20at%20a%20specialty%20soccer%20store.%20(I%20asked%20Dick's%20Sporting%20Goods%20to%20tell%20me%20more%20about%20the%20trend%20and%20will%20update%20this%20story%20if%20I%20hear%20back.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHacky%20Sack%20%E2%80%94%20capital%20%26quot%3BH%2C%26quot%3B%20capital%20%26quot%3BS%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20is%20actually%20trademarked%20by%20the%20company%20that%20owns%20the%20Wham-O%20line%20of%20toys.%20It's%20become%20so%20common%20that%20people%20use%20the%20name%20as%20a%20generic%20term%2C%20like%20Band-Aid%20or%20Q-tip.%20Wham-o%20had%20six%2C%2012-%20and%2015-packs%20of%20%26quot%3BPremium%20Suede%20Hacky%20Sacks%26quot%3B%20on%20its%20site%20(six%20for%20%2439.99)%2C%20but%20they%20were%20sold%20out.%20(I%20asked%20Wham-o%20for%20comment%2C%20but%20haven't%20heard%20back.%20I'll%20update%20this%20story%20if%20I%20do.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20also%20seen%20a%20few%20new%20online%20sellers%20of%20generic%20footbags.%20I%20talked%20to%20someone%20who%20opened%20an%20online%20store%20just%20five%20days%20ago.%20He%20said%20he's%20selling%201%2C000%20to%202%2C000%20per%20day%2C%20but%20I%20couldn't%20verify%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20Clarke%2C%20she%20said%20she%20is%20thrilled%20that%20her%20kids%20are%20into%20hacky%20sacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20outside%2C%20they're%20off%20their%20devices%2C%20they're%20socializing%2C%20they're%20connecting%20with%20their%20friends.%20To%20me%2C%20that%20is%20such%20a%20win%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BI%20applaud%20that%20so%20much%20as%20a%20parent%20who%20is%20dealing%20with%20parenting%20in%20this%20digital%20age.%20It's%20so%20refreshing%20to%20see%2C%20and%20I%20love%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhacky-sack-footbag-newest-trend-high-school-gen-z-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778324521000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fe506fba7ef34b41f369c7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhacky-sack-footbag-newest-trend-high-school-gen-z-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Gen%20X%20college%20staple%20is%20the%20hottest%20trend%20sweeping%20high%20schools.%20It's%20the%20hacky%20sack.%20They're%20sold%20out%20all%20over.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22knotopoulos%40businessinsider.com%20(Katie%20Notopoulos)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A99%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pak%20General's%20'Why%20English%3F'%20Jab%20At%20Indian%20Army%20Backfires%20Into%20Meme%20Fest%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22Operation%20Sindoor%20was%20launched%20last%20year%20after%20the%20Pahalgam%20terror%20attack%20in%20which%2026%20people%20were%20killed.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778324490000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2026-01%2F3irgrcvc_pak-army-spox_625x300_07_January_26.jpg%3Fim%3DFeatureCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Foperation-sindoor-pak-generals-why-english-jab-at-indian-army-backfires-into-meme-fest-11471042%23publisher%3Dnewsstand%22%2C%22summary%