ar-aged%20Chivas%20Regal%20whiskey%20that%20he%20created%20in%20collaboration%20with%20the%20brand.%20It's%20fitting%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmiami-grand-prix-distinct-features-f1-race-marina-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFormula%201%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20drivers%20are%20just%20as%20much%20a%20part%20of%20the%20luxury%20experience%20as%20the%20racing%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20organized%20a%20trip%20to%20Scotland%20with%20all%20of%20my%20childhood%20best%20friends%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20of%20creating%20the%20drink%2C%20which%20is%20a%20blend%20of%2016%20whiskies%2C%20a%20nod%20to%20his%20race%20number.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20very%2C%20very%2C%20fun%20weekend.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20sort%20of%20how%20I%20felt%20leaving%20Miami%20after%20my%20first-ever%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmiami-grand-prix-f1-with-kids-tips-what-to-know-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFormula%201%20race%20at%20Hard%20Rock%20Stadium%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Seriously%2C%20where%20have%20I%20been%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20loud%20hum%20of%20the%20cars%20driving%20around%20the%203.7-mile%20race%20track%2C%20the%20unmistakable%20signs%20of%20luxury%20from%20spectators%2C%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20mansplaining%20%E2%80%94%20which%20I%20didn't%20mind%20this%20time%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20one%20of%20the%20best%20weekends%20I've%20had%20in%20a%20while.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20first%20timer%2C%20the%20most%20memorable%20moments%20to%20me%20extended%20far%20beyond%20the%20track.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20I%20had%20sticker%20shock%20when%20I%20walked%20into%20the%20merch%20tent.%20Jackets%2C%20sweaters%2C%20and%20other%20items%20cost%20upward%20of%20%24200.%20Still%2C%20I%20was%20relieved%20to%20find%20stylish%20offerings%20for%20around%20%2450%2C%20including%20T-shirts%20and%20hats%20that%20anyone%20back%20home%20would%20love.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20heat.%20I%20mean%2C%20it%20is%20Miami%2C%20but%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cem%3Ethe%20heat%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Unless%20you%20paid%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20for%20access%20to%20The%20Paddock%20Club%20or%20similarly%20shaded%20areas%2C%20you%20were%20left%20battling%20the%20relentless%20sunrays.%20In%20Miami%2C%20even%20shade%20felt%20like%20a%20luxury%20amenity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbi-today-saturday-newsletter-formula-one-grand-prix-luxury-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778324402000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fe2b1ac9dd4cb81cda8a64%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbi-today-saturday-newsletter-formula-one-grand-prix-luxury-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20this%20Saturday%20edition%20of%20Business%20Insider%20Today%2C%20we're%20talking%20about%20all%20the%20luxury%20on%20display%20at%20the%20F1%20Miami%20Grand%20Prix.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jmckenzie%40businessinsider.com%20(Joi-Marie%20McKenzie)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bissell%20Pet%20Hair%20Eraser%20DualBrush%20review%3A%20The%20best%20vacuum%20we've%20tested%20for%20pet%20hair%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20buy%20through%20our%20links%2C%20Business%20Insider%20may%20earn%20an%20affiliate%20commission.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-reviews-expertise-in-product-reviews%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELearn%20more%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22side%20by%20side%20of%20a%20dog%20on%20a%20sofa%20with%20a%20vacuum%2C%20and%20a%20woman%20cleaning%20the%20sofa%20with%20the%20vacuum%20attachment%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f524a89a23d20d291b5a1f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFor%20deep%20cleaning%20and%20tackling%20pet%20hair%2C%20the%20Bissell%20Pet%20Hair%20Eraser%20DualBrush%20Vacuum%20is%20up%20to%20the%20task%2C%20with%20tangle-resistant%20brushes%20and%20HEPA%20filtration.%3Cp%3EErica%20Puisis%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPet%20parents%20know%20how%20quickly%20fur%2C%20dirt%2C%20and%20scattered%20debris%20can%20take%20over%20a%20home.%20But%20not%20every%20vacuum%20is%20built%20to%20handle%20the%20mess.%20I'm%20tired%20of%20vacuums%20that%20struggle%20to%20pick%20up%20hair%20from%20furniture%2C%20wrap%20hair%20around%20the%20brush%20roll%2C%20or%20fill%20up%20too%20quickly%20to%20finish%20the%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEnter%20the%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3Fh%3D35ccea79740a445cba4a69a8cbf13887cc1f433909beea597b87f38e7cf365ce%26postID%3D69f52198d17822f7a339a769%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fbissell-pet-hair-eraser-dualbrush-vacuum-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FBissell-Self-Cleaning-Technology-Headlights-42943%252Fdp%252FB0G3R8YTSH%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBissell%20Pet%20Hair%20Eraser%20DualBrush%20Vacuum%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20%24300%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-upright-vacuums%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eupright%20vacuum%20cleaner%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20designed%20to%20solve%20those%20problems.%20It's%20a%20workhorse%20on%20your%20floors%20with%20a%20lift-away%20canister%20that%20gives%20you%20good%20reach%20for%20stairs%20or%20above-floor%20cleaning.%20It%20is%20the%20latest%20addition%20to%20the%20Bissell%20line-up%2C%20created%20to%20capture%20pet%20hair%20anywhere%20it%20lurks%20(even%20in%20the%20crevices%20of%20your%20couch)%2C%20featuring%20powerful%20suction%20and%20Bissell's%20first%20new%20dual%20brushroll%20design%20that%20is%20intended%20to%20capture%20debris%20without%20annoying%20hair%20wrap.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20testing%20the%20Bissell%20Pet%20Hair%20Eraser%20DualBrush%20Vacuum%20against%20fur%2C%20debris%2C%20and%20dirt%20from%20two%20cats%20and%20a%20dog%2C%20I%20think%20that%20it's%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-pet-vacuum%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20vacuum%20for%20pet%20hair%3C%2Fa%3E%20thanks%20to%20its%20powerful%20suction%2C%20hair%20wrap%20resistance%2C%20HEPA%20filtration%2C%20and%20actually%20useful%20attachments.%20Its%20main%20drawbacks%20are%20noise%20and%20weight%2C%20but%20swivel%20steering%20helps%20make%20it%20easier%20to%20manage.%20All%20things%20considered%2C%20this%20mid-range%20upright%20vacuum%20shines%20as%20one%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-vacuum%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20vacuums%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Keep%20reading%20to%20find%20out%20why%20I%20think%20it's%20worth%20adding%20to%20your%20cleaning%20closet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220124321d-28c0-46b8-9c35-aca235a070db%5C%22%3EFirst%20impressions%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bissell%20vacuum%20floorhead%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f525883022d9b19bbffc1b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThis%20is%20Bissell's%20first%20DualBrush%20design%2C%20which%20features%20a%20soft%20brush%20and%20bristle%20roller%20to%20resist%20hair%20wrap%20and%20tackle%20all%20types%20of%20debris.%3Cp%3EErica%20Puisis%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBissell's%20newest%20upright%20vacuum%20cleaner%20requires%20very%20little%20assembly%2C%20requiring%20only%20a%20few%20pieces%20to%20click%20together.%20Compared%20to%20some%20other%20Bissell%20models%20that%20require%20the%20use%20of%20a%20screwdriver%20during%20set-up%2C%20this%20one%20intuitively%20comes%20together.%20The%20vacuum%20feels%20sturdy%20despite%20its%20mostly%20plastic%20construction%2C%20with%20a%20matte%20finish%20that%20doesn't%20show%20dust%20easily%2C%20giving%20it%20a%20premium%20feel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22lift-off%20pod%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f525889a23d20d291b5a23%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20lift-off%20pod%20is%20helpful%20for%20above%20floor%20tasks%20like%20the%20couch%20or%20stairs.%3Cp%3EErica%20Puisis%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20vacuum%20features%20a%20lift-off%20pod%20that%20houses%20the%20dustbin%20and%20motor%20and%20detaches%20for%20above-floor%20cleaning%20%E2%80%94%20a%20useful%20feature%20for%20stairs%20and%20furniture%20that%20not%20all%20upright%20vacuums%20offer.%20The%20cleaner%20head%20uses%20a%20dual-brush-roll%20system%E2%80%94a%20bristled%20roller%20for%20carpets%20and%20a%20soft%20roller%20for%20hard%20floors%20at%20the%20front%E2%80%94so%20you%20can%20move%20between%20surfaces%20without%20making%20manual%20adjustments.%20This%20is%20a%20first%20for%20Bissell%2C%20and%20it's%20also%20specifically%20designed%20to%20reduce%20hair%20wrap%2C%20which%20is%20a%20common%20frustration%20with%20pet%20vacuums.%20A%20slightly%20raised%20lip%20makes%20it%20better%20for%20suctioning%20up%20larger%20debris%2C%20too%2C%20while%20extra-bright%20LED%20headlights%20increase%20visibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2295cbeb57-55ff-4329-9349-9147a1bfeaf5%5C%22%3EHow%20it%20cleans%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225302%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20cat%20resting%20next%20to%20a%20vacuum%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f526929a23d20d291b5a2c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223976%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Bissell%20Pet%20Hair%20Eraser%20DualBrush%20proves%20itself%20capable%20of%20cleaning%20up%20after%20a%20home%20full%20of%20animals.%3Cp%3EErica%20Puisis%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22af29e1c3-1762-4f56-80c5-84b3365fc06d%5C%22%3EEveryday%20messes%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20daily%20cleaning%2C%20the%20Bissell%20Pet%20Hair%20Eraser%20is%20equally%20capable%20at%20cleaning%20hard%20floors%20and%20carpeting.%20The%20floor%20head%20automatically%20detects%20hard%20surface%20floors%20and%20slows%20the%20brush%20roll%20(to%20prevent%20scattering%20debris%20everywhere)%2C%20meaning%20I%20can%20move%20seamlessly%20from%20carpeted%20areas%20to%20hard%20floors%20without%20much%20thought%20to%20settings.%20For%20most%20cleaning%20runs%20around%20my%20home%2C%20I%20left%20the%20vacuum%20on%20the%20lowest%20suction%20setting%20(intended%20for%20bare%20floors%20and%20low%20pile%20carpets).%20When%20it%20was%20time%20to%20take%20on%20a%20thick%20area%20rug%2C%20I%20boosted%20the%20suction%20using%20the%20slider%20control%20on%20the%20vacuum's%20handle%20and%20the%20vacuum%20responded%20with%20extra%20oomph%20for%20pulling%20up%20cat%20hair%20and%20other%20debris.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20vacuum%20handled%20high-traffic%20areas%20like%20the%20kitchen%20and%20entryway%20well%2C%20often%20leaving%20floors%20noticeably%20cleaner%20in%20a%20single%20pass%2C%20and%20didn't%20clog%20on%20a%20low-pile%20rug%20or%20high-pile%20carpet.%20During%20testing%2C%20I%20challenged%20the%20vacuum%20to%20clean%20up%20small%20and%20large%20debris%20on%20multiple%20surfaces.%20I%20found%20that%20the%20vacuum%20sometimes%20scattered%20small%20debris%2C%20like%20rice%2C%20requiring%20a%20second%20pass%20to%20fully%20pick%20it%20up%20%E2%80%94%20something%20to%20keep%20in%20mind%20if%20you%20frequently%20deal%20with%20litter.%20Though%20for%20very%20fine%20debris%2C%20like%20hair%20or%20baking%20soda%2C%20the%20vacuum%20picked%20up%20the%20mess%20in%20a%20single%20pass.%20Larger%20debris%2C%20such%20as%20kibble%20or%20Cheerios%2C%20are%20captured%20by%20the%20vacuum%20in%20one%20or%20two%20passes.%20In%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20tests%2C%20the%20vacuum%20captured%20all%20of%20the%20debris%20%E2%80%94%20and%20sometimes%20even%20more%2C%20which%20is%20a%20testament%20to%20its%20suction%20power.%20However%2C%20the%209.8-inch%20cleaner%20head%20lacks%20a%20dedicated%20edge-cleaning%20brush%2C%20so%20debris%20along%20the%20walls%20occasionally%20needs%20an%20extra%20pass.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2255b52f53-1680-415f-a62c-d5e051d554c2%5C%22%3EHow%20it%20handles%20pet%20hair%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20an%20area%20rug%20that%20has%20seen%20its%20fair%20share%20of%20cat%20naps%20from%20a%20pair%20of%20heavy-shedding%20felines%2C%20I%20was%20impressed%20by%20the%20amount%20of%20embedded%20fur%20this%20upright%20vacuum%20extracted%20without%20clogging%20or%20wrapping%20around%20the%20brushroll.%20The%20difference%20in%20the%20rug's%20appearance%20was%20noticeable%20(and%20a%20bit%20embarrassing%20to%20realize%20its%20former%20condition).%20On%20medium-pile%20carpet%2C%20the%20vacuum%20performed%20similarly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHair%20wrap%20is%20also%20a%20non-issue.%20I%20specifically%20tested%20it%20with%20long%20strands%20of%20hair%20and%2C%20even%20after%20repeated%20use%2C%20the%20brush%20roll%20stayed%20clear.%20I%20haven't%20had%20to%20cut%20any%20strands%20free.%20That's%20a%20noticeable%20improvement%20over%20many%20vacuums%20that%20require%20regular%20maintenance%20to%20remove%20tangles%2C%20and%20even%20other%20Bissell%20vacuums%20I've%20come%20across.%20Pet%20owners%20will%20love%20how%20the%20dualbrush%20rolls%20and%20anti-tangle%20design%20means%20less%20time%20dealing%20with%20hair%20clogs%20and%20compromises%20in%20suction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a2b863aa-2c6f-477a-a196-b266c6c4af80%5C%22%3EUsing%20the%20attachments%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20turbobrush%20cleans%20pet%20hair%20on%20a%20couch%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f527353022d9b19bbffc30%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20motorized%20LED%20Turbobrush%20made%20it%20effortless%20to%20pick%20up%20pet%20hair%20from%20a%20sofa%2C%20with%20the%20option%20to%20illuminate%20the%20space%20with%20LED%20lights.%3Cp%3EErica%20Puisis%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Bissell%20Pet%20Hair%20Eraser's%20functionality%20is%20enhanced%20by%20its%20included%20attachments%3A%20a%20Pet%20TurboEraser%20tool%20and%20a%20Dusting%20Brush%2FCrevice%20Combo%20Tool%2C%20both%20of%20which%20feature%20an%20integrated%20LED%20light.%20Initially%2C%20I%20wondered%20if%20just%20two%20attachments%20would%20be%20sufficient%2C%20but%20I%20haven't%20felt%20like%20anything%20is%20missing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20particularly%20love%20the%20fact%20that%20both%20tools%20store%20onboard.%20I%20like%20having%20the%20crevice%20tool%20with%20me%20when%20vacuuming%20in%20the%20kitchen%20because%20I%20could%20immediately%20suction%20up%20crumbs%20or%20dust%20from%20under%20the%20lip%20of%20my%20oven%20range%20or%20refrigerator%20as%20I%20pass%20through.%20I%20found%20the%20Pet%20TurboEraser%20tool%20particularly%20useful%20for%20picking%20up%20pet%20hair%20on%20an%20armchair%20and%20a%20large%20sectional%20in%20a%20single%20pass.%20Both%20have%20an%20integrated%20LED%20light%2C%20which%20helps%20spot%20debris%20more%20easily%2C%20especially%20in%20shadowy%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c48ee5b5-d1f8-4acc-a36d-519572ce8431%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20it's%20like%20to%20use%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20woman%20holds%20a%20vacuum%20in%20her%20hand%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f528599a23d20d291b5a37%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFor%20an%20upright%2C%20the%2017%20pound%20feels%20manueverable%20and%20well-balanced.%3Cp%3EErica%20Puisis%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20typically%20a%20bit%20biased%20toward%20cordless%20vacuums%20for%20their%20grab-and-go%20convenience%2C%20but%20the%20Bissell%20Pet%20Hair%20Eraser%20Dual%20Clean%20Vacuum%20is%20very%20comfortable%20to%20use.%20It%20maneuvers%20smoothly%20around%20furniture%20thanks%20to%20its%20swivel%20steering.%20At%2017%20pounds%2C%20it's%20heavier%20than%20a%20stick%20vacuum%2C%20but%20the%20weight%20feels%20well-balanced%20in%20use.%20On%20hard%20floors%2C%20it%20glides%20easily%2C%20and%20while%20it's%20more%20noticeable%20on%20thicker%20carpet%2C%20it%20never%20feels%20difficult%20to%20control.%20LED%20headlights%20on%20the%20floorhead%20are%20especially%20helpful%20for%20spotting%20dust%20and%20pet%20hair%20under%20furniture%20or%20in%20dim%20areas%2C%20making%20it%20easier%20to%20see%20which%20areas%20need%20more%20attention.%20The%2030-foot%20cord%20also%20offers%20excellent%20reach%2C%20so%20I%20didn't%20need%20to%20frequently%20pause%20to%20plug%20the%20vacuum%20into%20a%20new%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20standout%20feature%20of%20this%20Bissell%20model%20is%20the%20detachable%20canister.%20Described%20as%20a%20Lift-Off%20Pod%2C%20I%20found%20this%20function%20very%20useful%20for%20cleaning%20pet%20hair%20and%20debris%20from%20furniture.%20Essentially%2C%20I%20could%20park%20the%20vacuum%2C%20carry%20the%20canister%20to%20a%20spot%20near%20a%20couch%20or%20chair%2C%20and%20get%20to%20work%20with%20the%20pet%20hair%20attachment%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20flexible%20vacuum%20hose.%20This%20functionality%20is%20also%20great%20for%20stairs%2C%20which%20can%20be%20a%20cleaning%20challenge%20for%20upright%20vacuum%20cleaners%20that%20don't%20fit%20on%20steps.%20In%20this%20case%2C%20the%20Bissell's%20Lift-Off%20Pod%20can%20rest%20on%20a%20nearby%20step%20as%20you%20work%2C%20and%20the%20vacuum%20cleaner%20body%20can%20stay%20parked%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20stairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompared%20to%20other%20pet%20vacuums%20I%20tested%2C%20this%20model%20was%20among%20the%20loudest%20%E2%80%94%20registering%20at%20about%2080%20decibels%20(about%2060%20to%2085%20decibels%20is%20typical).%20That%20said%2C%20I%20didn't%20find%20the%20noise%20high-pitched%20or%20a%20nuisance%20to%20deal%20with.%20The%20vacuum's%20HEPA%20filtration%20also%20means%20that%20as%20you%20use%20the%20vacuum%2C%20it's%20trapping%20dust%20and%20pet%20dander%20inside.%20That's%20a%20big%20plus%20for%20pet%20owners%20in%20general%20and%20allergy%20sufferers%20in%20particular.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22afe075b6-c51d-41a9-858a-3f005ed13336%5C%22%3EMaintenance%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%201.25-liter%20dustbin%20offers%20less%20capacity%20than%20upright%20vacuums%20with%20a%201.5-liter%20or%20larger%20dustbin.%20That%20being%20said%2C%20my%20cleaning%20run%20was%20always%20finished%20before%20the%20dust%20bin%20reached%20capacity.%20Emptying%20the%20bin%20is%20quick%20and%20easy%20since%20using%20a%20push-button%20release.%20In%20my%20experience%2C%20the%20debris%20falls%20out%20cleanly%20without%20needing%20to%20reach%20inside%2C%20so%20that's%20a%20win.%20I%20do%20wish%20the%20release%20button%20were%20positioned%20higher%20on%20the%20bin%20for%20easier%20emptying%2C%20but%20this%20is%20a%20minor%20quibble%20given%20the%20vacuum's%20overall%20well-planned%20design.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20regular%20use%2C%20I%20haven't%20needed%20to%20clean%20the%20brush%20roll%20yet%2C%20holding%20up%20to%20its%20claim%20of%20resisting%20hair%20wrap.%20Though%20if%20you%20do%20need%20to%20access%20it%2C%20removal%20requires%20removing%20seven%20Phillips-head%20screws%2C%20which%20isn't%20as%20convenient%20as%20a%20tool-free%20design.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaintenance%20is%20minimal%20overall.%20The%20dustbin%20and%20pre-motor%20filter%20can%20be%20rinsed%20clean%2C%20while%20the%20post-motor%20filter%20just%20needs%20occasional%20tapping%20and%20replacement%20about%20every%20six%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c2d42f5b-9727-4f40-b909-8b95d851a9de%5C%22%3ECons%20to%20consider%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bissell%20vacuum%20with%20cheerios%20inside%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f52588ab24bc0b23a189ee%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBeyond%20its%20weight%20and%20noise%2C%20sometimes%20larger%20pieces%20of%20debris%20took%20a%20second%20pass%20to%20suction%20up.%3Cp%3EErica%20Puisis%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20drawback%20of%20this%20vacuum%20is%20its%20noise%20factor.%20I%20didn't%20feel%20comfortable%20using%20the%20vacuum%20while%20my%20husband%20was%20on%20the%20phone%20or%20late%20at%20night%20(we%20share%20a%20wall%20with%20a%20neighbor).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20weight%20isn't%20a%20huge%20consideration%20if%20you%20have%20a%20one-level%20floor%20plan%20since%20the%20vacuum%20wheels%20around%20so%20effortlessly.%20But%20if%20you%20do%20frequently%20carry%20your%20vacuum%20up%20and%20down%20several%20flights%20of%20stairs%2C%20its%2017-pound%20weight%20is%20something%20you%20might%20want%20to%20consider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2238094c12-6583-4848-9dc2-c78f88b7a0ad%5C%22%3EWhat%20are%20your%20alternatives%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20holds%20the%20Shark%20Stratos%20Upright%20vacuum%20in%20a%20living%20room%20with%20carpet%20at%20a%20side%20profile.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F656a2f9158e7c0c29a28dc2f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EShark%20was%20the%20first%20to%20offer%20a%20dual%20brushroll%20design%2C%20as%20seen%20on%20its%20Shark%20Stratos%2C%20a%20comparable%20option.%3Cp%3ECamryn%20Rabideau%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20prefer%20a%20cordless%20option%2C%20Bissell%20also%20released%20the%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3Fh%3D75469f3bed56f049049eaf1