0Buffett%20fans%20outside%20of%20his%20home.%3Cp%3ETheron%20Mohamed%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%20morning%2C%20I%20took%20an%20Uber%20to%20Buffett's%20home%2C%20around%20a%2010-minute%20drive%20west%20of%20the%20city.%20The%20investor%20purchased%20the%20house%20for%20%2431%2C500%20in%201958%20and%20has%20resided%20there%20ever%20since.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20watched%20a%20steady%20stream%20of%20people%20arrive%20by%20car%2C%20walk%20around%20the%20investor's%20family%20home%2C%20pose%20for%20a%20few%20pictures%2C%20then%20depart.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20struck%20me%20as%20remarkable%20that%20a%20billionaire's%20home%20address%20is%20public%20information%2C%20and%20anyone%20can%20visit%20his%20leafy%20suburban%20neighborhood%20and%20try%20to%20catch%20a%20glimpse%20of%20him%20through%20his%20hedges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrashant%20Dugar%20and%20Anand%20Behl%20were%20posing%20for%20photos%20with%20their%20Buffett%20Squishmallow%20outside%20his%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20asked%20why%20they'd%20come%2C%20Behl%20joked%20it%20was%20like%20%26quot%3Basking%20why%20are%20Christians%20at%20Jesus'%20birthplace.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuffett%20lies%20at%20the%20%26quot%3Bintersection%20of%20human%20excellence%20and%20human%20values%2C%26quot%3B%20Behl%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20look%20for%20heroes%20in%20life%2C%20right%3F%26quot%3B%20Dugar%20added%2C%20noting%20that%20Buffett%20is%20one%20of%20the%20very%20few%20people%20in%20finance%20who%20make%20the%20cut.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pair%20told%20me%20that%20Buffett's%20choice%20of%20home%20speaks%20to%20his%20core%20values%20such%20as%20humility%20and%20frugality%2C%20his%20desire%20to%20avoid%20the%20noise%20and%20distractions%20that%20come%20with%20luxury%20and%20big-city%20life%2C%20and%20his%20long-term%20investing%20approach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThere%20was%20no%20escaping%20Buffett%2C%20even%20at%20the%20airport.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%