%20said%20its%20technology%20wouldn't%20be%20where%20it%20is%20now%20without%20its%20experience%20helping%20Ukraine%20stop%20Russian%20drone%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERobin%20Radar%2C%20a%20Dutch%20firm%20that%20makes%20drone%20detection%20radar%20systems%2C%20has%20had%20systems%20in%20Ukraine%20since%202023%2C%20and%20now%2C%20its%20products%20are%20increasingly%20being%20used%20in%20the%20Middle%20East.%20It%20says%20it%20rapidly%20developed%20an%20upgrade%20to%20help%20US%20allies%20there%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20lessons%20learned%20on%20Ukrainian%20battlefields.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20upgraded%20its%20radars%20in%20Ukraine%20to%20detect%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspeed-ukraine-battlefield-development-pushes-weapons-makers-modular-software-first-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elarger%20attack%20drones%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20longer%20ranges%20as%20Russia%20escalated%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-building-500-shahed-drones-per-day-volodymyr-zelenskyy-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emass%20drone%20bombardments%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Robin%20Radar%20used%20Ukrainian%20feedback%20to%20upgrade%20its%20systems%20to%20detect%20those%20drones%20from%20much%20further%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKristian%20Brost%2C%20the%20general%20manager%20for%20Robin%20Radar%20in%20the%20US%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20being%20in%20Ukraine%20was%20key%20to%20the%20company's%20ability%20to%20detect%20those%20larger%20objects%20at%20longer%20ranges.%20He%20said%20Ukrainian%20commanders%20regularly%20gave%20feedback%20on%20operational%20needs%2C%20while%20a%20dedicated%20task%20force%20collected%20battlefield%20data%20to%20refine%20the%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20the%20data%20we've%20gotten%20from%20Ukraine%20has%20been%20very%20important%20for%20us%26quot%3B%20and%20how%20the%20company%20makes%20and%20upgrades%20its%20products%2C%20Brost%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20that%20ability%20is%20needed%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20where%20the%20company%20says%20its%20flagship%20IRIS%20radar%20is%20stationed%20in%20multiple%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIran%20has%20been%20firing%20missiles%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Firan-shahed-drone-interceptor-booming-business-manufacturers-middle-east-t2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EShahed%20drones%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20targets%20across%20the%20region%20in%20recent%20months%20amid%20fighting%20with%20the%20US%20and%20Israel.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThat%20kind%20of%20drone%20is%20one%20that%20Ukraine%20and%20the%20companies%20working%20in%20the%20country%20are%20combating.%20Russia%20has%20fired%20Iranian-designed%20Shahed%20drones%20at%20Ukraine%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-new-turbojet-drone-geran-5-american-chinese-german-parts-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edomestically%20produced%20version%3C%2Fa%3E%20called%20the%20Geran.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22People%20look%20up%20at%20a%20large%20black%20drone%20on%20display%20in%20front%20of%20a%20blue%20and%20white%20church%20with%20a%20gold%20top%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fdff6aba7ef34b41f36631%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EExperience%20against%20Shahed-style%20drones%20in%20Ukraine%20is%20now%20in%20demand.%3Cp%3EGenya%20SAVILOV%20%2F%20AFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESiete%20Hamminga%2C%20Robin%20Radar's%20CEO%2C%20said%20that%20Iran%20is%20%26quot%3Breally%20following%20exactly%20the%20same%20patterns%26quot%3B%20that%20Russia%20has%20in%20Ukraine.%20He%20called%20it%20%26quot%3Banother%20wake-up%20call%20for%20Western%20society%26quot%3B%20to%20be%20ready%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-shot-down-shahed-drones-helping-middle-east-zelenskyy-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edrone%20warfare%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Iran%20war%20has%20sparked%20new%20interest%20in%20the%20radars.%20The%20company%20said%20this%20week%20that%20it%20has%20delivered%20its%20IRIS%20counter-UAS%20radars%20to%20the%20Gulf%20region%20within%20weeks%20of%20their%20order%20and%20that%20it%20is%20expanding%20manufacturing%20to%20support%20countries%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHamminga%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Esaid%20the%20company%20was%20already%20active%20in%20Jordan%20before%20the%20Iran%20war%2C%20but%20it%20has%20seen%20new%20traction%20with%20other%20countries%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20direct%20result%20of%20the%20war.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERobin%20Radar%20also%20works%20in%20the%20US%2C%20including%20partnering%20with%20the%20Department%20of%20Homeland%20Security%20for%20counter-drone%20protection%20of%20the%20World%20Cup.%20It%20attributes%20its%20work%20in%20Ukraine%20to%20its%20US%20presence%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20it%20wasn't%20for%20Ukraine%20and%20all%20the%20work%20we%20did%20there%2C%20we%20probably%20wouldn't%20have%20the%20products%20that%20we%20do%20have%20in%20North%20America%2C%26quot%3B%20Brost%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWestern%20defense%20companies%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwestern-defense-companies-set-up-operations-in-ukraine-war-continues-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epushing%20to%20have%20a%20presence%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Ukraine%20to%20learn%20how%20to%20best%20work%20on%20the%20battlefield%20and%20to%20get%20a%20battle-proven%20status.%20It's%20seen%20as%20key%20to%20having%20weaponry%20that's%20able%20to%20work%20in%20large-scale%2C%20modern%20warfare%20that's%20rapidly%20changing%2C%20and%20where%20weaponry%20needs%20to%20stay%20up-to-date%2C%20too.%20Officials%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdrone-companies-without-ukraine-battlefield-presence-give-up-uk-2025%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esee