djacent%20bets.%20KKR's%202023%20investment%20in%20data-center%20cooling%20firm%20Cool-It%20netted%20a%2015%20times%20return%20when%20Ecolab%20bought%20it%20for%20%244.75%20billion%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20KKR's%20best-performing%20investments%20ever%2C%20the%20sale%20also%20returned%20an%20average%20of%20%24240%2C000%20to%20the%20firm's%20640%20employees%20as%20part%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworkers-kkr-company-geostabilization-payouts-private-equity-ownership-works-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EKKR's%20broader%20employee-ownership%20initiatives%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20at%20Ares%2C%20its%20investments%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-invests-in-nuclear-for-aws-following-google-and-microsoft-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emodular%20nuclear%20reactor%20company%20X-Energy%3C%2Fa%3E%20may%20soon%20pay%20off.%20The%20company%20went%20public%20with%20a%20%241%20billion%20IPO%20late%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20transaction%20was%20the%20%26quot%3Blargest%20equity%20offering%20ever%20for%20a%20nuclear%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20CEO%20Michael%20Arougheti%2C%20with%20the%20firm's%20roughly%20%24100%20million%20investment%20now%20worth%20nearly%20%24700%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2250d8f41f-8b11-4c22-b8f2-d5458a35d4d8%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20angles%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20longtime%20participants%20are%20taking%20new%20approaches%20to%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlackstone%20is%20launching%20a%20publicly%20traded%20company%20that%20will%20buy%20newly%20built%20hyperscale%20data%20centers.%20Blackstone's%20data-center%20REIT%2C%20Blackstone%20Digital%20Infrastructure%20Trust%2C%20filed%20for%20an%20IPO%20on%20Monday%20and%20plans%20to%20raise%20%241.75%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20company%20will%20help%20bring%20the%20private-market%20data%20center%20development%20bet%20to%20the%20publi