en%20known%20since%202022%2C%20when%20Business%20Insider%20broke%20the%20news%20that%20he%20was%20the%20father%20of%20the%20twin%20son%20and%20daughter%20she'd%20had%20the%20year%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20sometimes%20emotional%20testimony%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20Zilis%20revealed%20new%20details%2C%20describing%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshivon-zilis-clears-the-air-around-her-relationship-with-elon-musk-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eon-and-off%20romantic%20relationship%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20began%20in%202016%2C%20the%20year%20she%20joined%20OpenAI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20told%20jurors%20that%20in%202021%2C%20she%20accepted%20Musk's%20offer%20to%20be%20a%20sperm-donor%20father.%20The%20twins%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-shivon-zilis-secret-twins-neuralink-tesla%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eborn%20via%20IVF%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20she%20said%2C%20and%20she%20was%20fine%20with%20him%20having%20no%20role%20in%20raising%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Bencouraging%20everyone%20around%20him%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpronatalism-elon-musk-population-tech-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eto%20have%20kids%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20testified.%20He%20told%20her%2C%20%26quot%3BThat%20if%20I%20was%20ever%20interested%2C%20he'd%20be%20happy%20to%20make%20a%20donation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20initially%20agreed%20on%20complete%20confidentiality%20of%20the%20donation%2C%26quot%3B%20Zilis%20told%20the%20jury.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20just%20an%20insane%20kind%20of%2C%20just%20security%20risk%20that%20he%20bears%20with%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20would%20go%20on%20to%20father%20two%20more%20of%20Zilis'%20children%2C%20she%20said.%20And%20since%20the%20Business%20Insider%20story%2C%20he's%20been%20an%20active%20parent%20%E2%80%94%20when%20not%20in%20%26quot%3Bmaniac%20mode.%26quot%