ion-planning%20details%2C%20like%20checking%20hotel%20ratings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lowrie%20is%20holding%20a%20pint%20of%20beer.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fda449ba7ef34b41f363cd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELowrie%20now%20has%20more%20time%20for%20vacation%20planning%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Matt%20Lowrie%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20fun%2C%20I've%20set%20myself%20the%20challenge%20of%20seeing%20if%20I%20can%20pivot%20into%20data%20analytics%20for%20a%20sports%20team%2C%20because%20I%20love%20sports.%20It's%20an%20industry%20I%20don't%20know%20anything%20about%2C%20but%20I'm%20trying%20to%20make%20contacts.%20I%20like%20retirement%2C%20but%20I'd%20definitely%20say%20yes%20to%20a%20dream%20job%20like%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20grandfather's%20advice%20about%20investing%20for%20the%20long%20term%20and%20keeping%20as%20much%20of%20your%20investments%20as%20possible%20has%20helped%20me%20get%20where%20I%20am%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fadvice-grandfather-helped-retire-early-google-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778320741000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fe04ddba7ef34b41f3666e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fadvice-grandfather-helped-retire-early-google-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20former%20Googler%20assumed%20only%20people%20who%20got%20rich%20from%20their%20startups%20being%20bought%20out%20could%20retire%20early.%20He%20shared%20the%20simple%20investment%20strategies%20he%20says%20helped%20him%20do%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ccheong%40insider.com%20(Charissa%20Cheong)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ryan%20Cohen%20tells%20us%20why%20he's%20serious%20about%20buying%20eBay%20%E2%80%94%20and%20what%20he%20thinks%20about%20his%20viral%20CNBC%20interview%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225464%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ryan%20Cohen%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20GameStop%2C%20wears%20a%20white%20dress%20shirt%20and%20black%20jeans.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f8cde59a23d20d291b6123%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%227650%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BI%20did%20not%20want%20to%20be%20the%20CEO%20of%20GameStop.%20I%20want%20to%20be%20the%20CEO%20of%20eBay%2C%26quot%3B%20Ryan%20Cohen%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3Cp%3EGameStop%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EGameStop%20CEO%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgamestop-ceo-ryan-cohen-net-worth-career-history-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERyan%20Cohen%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20he%20will%20continue%20doing%20whatever%20it%20takes%20to%20buy%20eBay.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECNBC's%20skeptical%20interviewers%20%26quot%3Bmisunderstood%26quot%3B%20his%20deal%20math%20in%20his%20now-viral%20%26quot%3BSquawk%20Box%26quot%3B%20appearance%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20activist%20investor%20accused%20eBay's%20leadership%20of%20lacking%20%26quot%3Bskin%20in%20the%20game%26quot%3B%20and%20fostering%20a%20culture%20of%20day%20drinking.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ERyan%20Cohen%20says%20he%20never%20wanted%20to%20be%20CEO%20of%20GameStop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20he%20says%20he%20dreams%20of%20helming%20eBay%20and%20thinks%20he%20has%20a%20real%20shot%20at%20achieving%20that%20goal%2C%20despite%20critics'%20claims%20that%20the%20e-commerce%20giant%20is%20beyond%20his%20reach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20going%20to%20continue%20doing%20whatever%20I%20need%20to%20do%20in%20order%20to%20buy%20the%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20GameStop%20CEO%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20a%20phone%20interview%20on%20Friday.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20going%20to%20make%20myself%20CEO%20of%20both.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECohen%20surprised%20Wall%20Street%20earlier%20this%20week%20when%20he%20disclosed%20that%20GameStop%20had%20made%20an%20unsolicited%20bid%20of%20about%20%2456%20billion%20for%20eBay%2C%20which%20has%20a%20market%20value%20more%20than%20three%20times%20its%20size.%20He%20raised%20eyebrows%20again%20on%20Monday%20when%20he%20appeared%20on%20CNBC's%20%26quot%3BSquawk%20Box%2C%26quot%3B%20during%20which%20the%20hosts%20openly%20doubted%20whether%20the%20company%20could%20afford%20eBay%20and%20responded%20to%20his%20remarks%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgamestop-ceo-ryan-cohen-cnbc-interview-bizarre-moments-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexhalations%20and%20chuckles%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20sure%20whether%20their%20questions%20were%20sincere%20or%20not%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Cohen%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20laid%20out%20a%20clear%20explanation%20of%20how%20he%20would%20finance%20a%20deal%20for%20eBay.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20what%20is%20so%20complicated%20for%20them%20to%20figure%20it%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20CNBC%20spokesperson%20said%20the%20%26quot%3BSquawk%20Box%26quot%3B%20interview%20%26quot%3Bspeaks%20for%20itself.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECohen%2C%20whose%20%26quot%3Bhalf%20cash%2C%20half%20stock%26quot%3B%20mantra%20describing%20the%20financing%20quickly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgamestop-ceo-ebay-takeover-offer-ryan-cohen-memes-wsb-reactions-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebecame%20a%20meme%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20GameStop%20has%20about%20%249%20billion%20in%20cash%20and%20that%20TD%20Bank%20had%20expressed%20confidence%20in%20placing%20roughly%20%2420%20billion%20in%20debt.%20Together%2C%20he%20said%2C%20would%20cover%20the%20cash%20portion%20of%20the%20bid.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIn%20the%20wake%20of%20his%20viral%20CNBC%20appearance%2C%20Cohen%20offered%20a%20more%20detailed%20explanation%20of%20his%20math%2C%20including%20on%20TBPN.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20we're%20proposing%20is%20for%20existing%20shareholders%20to%20take%20half%20of%20their%20investment%20off%20the%20table%2C%20and%20that%20would%20be%20us%20providing%20them%20with%20%2428%20billion%2C%20which%20is%20like%20a%2040%25%20premium%20from%20when%20we%20started%20buying%20the%20stock%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20TBPN.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20then%20they%20would%20be%20getting%20roughly%20%E2%80%94%20I%20mean%20it%20depends%20on%20ultimately%20when%20the%20transaction%20closes%20%E2%80%94%20but%20they%20would%20be%20rolling%20the%20rest%20into%20the%20combined%20company%20of%20GameStop%20and%20eBay.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20speaking%20with%20Business%20Insider%2C%20Cohen%20suggested%20the%20stock%20component%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bearnings%20per%20share%20accretive%26quot%3B%20for%20GameStop%20shareholders%20because%20he%20said%20he%20could%20significantly%20increase%20eBay's%20profitability%20through%20cost-cutting%2C%20making%20the%20combined%20entities%20more%20valuable%20overall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220c8a8d2f-9938-445a-8be7-6e369e417ee4%5C%22%3EA%20familiar%20playbook%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20publicly%20criticizing%20eBay's%20leadership%20and%20arguing%20he%20could%20do%20a%20better%20job%2C%20Cohen%20borrowed%20from%20the%20playbook%20he%20used%20when%20he%20took%20over%20GameStop%20in%202022.%20A%20key%20difference%2C%20though%2C%20is%20that%20eBay's%20business%20is%20much%20healthier%20today%20than%20GameStop's%20was%20back%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECohen%2C%20who%20built%20his%20fortune%20as%20the%20cofounder%20of%20online%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchewy-cofounder-how-he-created-multibillion-dollar-empire-2019-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epet-products%20retailer%20Chewy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20eBay%20could%20be%20in%20an%20even%20better%20financial%20position%20if%20it%20were%20managed%20more%20efficiently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20ton%20of%20fat%20that%20can%20be%20cut%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20pointing%20to%20what%20he%20described%20as%20excessive%20operating%20expenses%20at%20a%20company%20that%20carries%20no%20inventory%20and%20whose%20operating%20income%20has%20remained%20roughly%20flat%20for%20a%20decade%20despite%20broader%20e-commerce%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECohen%20also%20took%20aim%20at%20eBay's%20executives%20and%20directors.%20He%20alleged%20they%20had%20sold%20%26quot%3Bhundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%20of%20stock%26quot%3B%20without%20buying%20shares%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20not%20owners%20in%20the%20business.%20They're%20just%20milking%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20simply%20a%20paycheck%20for%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20Cohen%20criticized%20eBay's%20corporate%20culture%2C%20alleging%20that%20the%20company%20had%20become%20too%20comfortable%20and%20undisciplined%20under%20its%20current%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20eBay%2C%20which%20has%20publicly%20said%20it%20is%20reviewing%20Cohen's%20bid%2C%20declined%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2293462978-632d-4087-b556-68bb16a4f79e%5C%22%3EA%20frugal%20'meme%20king'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECohen%2C%20who%20has%20also%20pushed%20for%20change%20at%20Nordstrom%20and%20Bed%20Bath%20%26amp%3B%20Beyond%2C%20said%20he%20wouldn't%20take%20a%20salary%20if%20he%20became%20CEO%20of%20eBay.%20He%20doesn't%20earn%20one%20at%20GameStop%2C%20though%20he%20has%20a%20%2435%20billion%20compensation%20package%20tied%20to%20hitting%20market%20cap%20and%20profit%20milestones%2C%20which%20an%20eBay%20deal%20could%20help%20unlock.%20He%20said%20he%20pays%20his%20personal%20assistant%20out%20of%20his%20own%20pocket%20and%20that%20whoever%20GameStop%20hires%20for%20a%20recently%20posted%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%