ls%2C%20the%20family%20has%20had%20the%20chance%20to%20see%20wild%20horses%20run%20in%20Arizona%20and%20build%20a%20community%20of%20friends%20on%20the%20road.%20Bailey%20saw%20a%20turtle%20and%20a%20dolphin%20while%20paddleboarding%20in%20Florida%2C%20and%20saw%20the%20northern%20lights%20on%20a%20date-night%20hike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAre%20you%20traveling%20the%20country%20by%20RV%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20this%20reporter%20to%20share%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Amhoff%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emhoff%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20family's%20journey%20reminds%20her%20of%20the%20late%20'90s%20Nickelodeon%20cartoon%20%26quot%3BThe%20Wild%20Thornberrys%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20featured%20a%20family%20traveling%20by%20RV%20and%20documenting%20animals.%20The%20family%2C%20as%20an%20homage%20to%20the%20show%2C%20styled%20their%20social%20media%20handles%20as%20%26quot%3Bwildthornbaileys.%26quot%3B%20They%20started%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fempty-nesters-sold-house-live-rv-full-time-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efull-time%20RV%20journey%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202019%2C%20but%20recently%20took%20a%20roughly%20one-year%20break%20while%20still%20doing%20RV%20life%20when%20they%20could.%20That%20gap%20is%20coming%20to%20an%20end%2C%20as%20they%20plan%20to%20hit%20the%20road%20this%20summer%20when%20the%20larger%20RV%20they%20bought%20and%20renovated%20is%20ready.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20has%20four%20kids%20%E2%80%94%20aged%208%2C%2010%2C%2013%2C%20and%2014%2C%20with%20the%20youngest%20being%20under%202%20when%20they%20first%20started%20RV%20life.%20Bailey%20said%20that%20almost%20losing%20one%20of%20their%20children%20to%20undiagnosed%20type%201%20diabetes%20prompted%20them%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frv-living-full-time-work-camp-sell-home-motorhome-job-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emove%20from%20a%20house%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20open%20road.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20realized%20we%20were%20both%20working%20nonstop%2C%20and%20we%20just%20wanted%20to%20spend%20more%20time%20with%20our%20kids%2C%26quot%3B%20Bailey%20said%2C%20who%20was%20a%20photographer%20largely%20working%20weekends%20and%20nights%20while%20her%20husband%20worked%20in%20construction.%20Her%20son's%20health%20scare%20inspired%20them%20to%20take%20a%20chance.%20%26quot%3BAll%20we%20could%20think%20about%20was%20all%20the%20things%20he%20hadn't%20done.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224864%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cassie%20Bailey's%20family%20in%20a%20mountain%20area%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fe187fc9dd4cb81cda89bd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223648%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20family%20has%20been%20able%20to%20see%20sights%20they%20wouldn't%20have%20from%20a%20stationary%20house.%3Cp%3ECassie%20Bailey%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20in%202019%2C%20they%20sold%20their%20house%20and%20most%20of%20their%20belongings%20to%20fund%20their%20new%20chapter.%20Bailey%20said%20it%20was%20scary%20to%20hit%20the%20road%20with%20four%20kids.%20But%20the%20family%2C%20who%20didn't%20travel%20much%20prior%20to%20RV%20life%2C%20has%20loved%20the%20adventures%20and%20new%20memories%20they've%20created.%20%26quot%3BI'll%20never%20sit%20at%20another%20hospital%20in%20a%20chair%20thinking%20all%20the%20regrets%20of%20things%20I%20didn't%20get%20to%20do%20with%20my%20kids%20and%20husband%2C%26quot%3B%20Bailey%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d1ba8dde-abf2-44f0-82f6-fe7434b1829e%5C%22%3EThere%20are%20ways%20to%20control%20spending%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBailey%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretired-baby-boomers-sold-their-home-to-pursue-rv-living-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERV%20life%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%20end%20up%20being%20more%20expensive%20than%20a%20house%20if%20you%20spend%20like%20you're%20on%20vacation%2C%20but%20that's%20not%20how%20the%20family%20lives%2C%20and%20they%20find%20it's%20been%20an%20affordable%20lifestyle.%20She%20said%20living%20in%20a%20house%20temporarily%20while%20they%20were%20waiting%20for%20their%20new%20RV%20was%20a%20big%20adjustment%20because%20they%20hadn't%20had%20to%20pay%20for%20electricity%20or%20water%20in%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20like%20to%20find%20all%20the%20ways%20to%20save%20money%20in%20any%20way%20possible%20so%20that%20we're%20able%20to%20fund%20our%20travels%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20Bailey%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20the%20cost%20of%20staying%20at%20campgrounds%20varies.%20They%20use%20membership%20programs%20like%20those%20offered%20by%20Thousand%20Trails%20and%20Passport%20America%20for%20deals.%20Otherwise%2C%20they%20will%20park%20in%20public%20spaces%20managed%20by%20the%20Bureau%20of%20Land%20Management.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20free%20areas%20without%20water%2C%20electric%2C%20or%20sewage%20hookups%20can%20be%20a%20way%20to%20save%20money%2C%20but%20it%20means%20they%20have%20to%20plan%2C%20packing%20additional%20water%20and%20other%20necessities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cassie%20Bailey's%20kids%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fe287ae1443b8dc48e357c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBailey's%20kids%20are%20growing%20up%20on%20the%20road.%3Cp%3ECassie%20Bailey%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgas-prices-high-how-to-save-money-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFuel%20can%20get%20expensive%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20RVers%20can%20stay%20at%20campgrounds%20or%20explore%20local%20spots%20for%20a%20while%20before%20returning%20to%20the%20road.%20However%2C%20Bailey%20said%20aspiring%20RVers%20should%20be%20mindful%20of%20rising%20prices.%20Her%20family%20uses%20Open%20Roads%2C%20a%20free%20fuel%20card%20that%20lets%20RVers%20save%20at%20participating%20locations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20also%20leverages%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcostco-employee-best-things-big-family-weekly-list-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECostco%20membership%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20food%2C%20since%20there%20are%20plenty%20of%20locations.%20They%20also%20like%20to%20shop%20at%20farmers%20markets%20and%20try%20to%20be%20mindful%20that%20prices%20can%20be%20higher%20in%20tourist%20locations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20do%20end%20up%20spending%20more%20on%20food%20when%20we're%20traveling%2C%20if%20we're%20not%20careful%2C%20especially%20if%20we%20eat%20out%20a%20lot%2C%20which%20is%20easy%20to%20do%20because%20you'll%20see%20these%20cute%20little%20places%2C%26quot%3B%20Bailey%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225973%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cassie%20Bailey's%20kids%20eating%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fe1875c9dd4cb81cda89bc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224480%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBailey's%20kids%20experience%20their%20first%20RV%20Thanksgiving.%3Cp%3ECassie%20Bailey%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20that%20because%20a%20lot%20of%20RVers%20work%20remote%20jobs%2C%20it's%20best%20to%20have%20as%20much%20internet%20access%20as%20possible%20in%20case%20one%20plan%20works%20better%20in%20certain%20conditions.%20Her%20family%20pays%20about%20%24100%20a%20month%20for%20OTR%2C%20a%20wireless%20internet%20service%20targeted%20to%20travelers%20and%20those%20in%20rural%20areas%2C%20and%20%24165%20a%20month%20for%20a%20Starlink%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20family%20has%20been%20through%20a%20few%20RVs%2C%20and%20is%20moving%20into%20their%20latest%20one%2C%20partly%20because%20the%20older%20children%20wanted%20their%20own%20space%20and%20privacy.%20In%20their%20last%20RV%2C%20all%20four%20kids%20were%20sharing%20a%20room%20with%