e%20conducted%20in%20August%2020234.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20do%20you%20usually%20wake%20up%20in%20the%20morning%3F%20Is%20it%20the%20doorbell%2C%20an%20alarm%2C%20or%20perhaps%20a%20family%20member%3F%20Now%2C%20imagine%20waking%20up%20to%20the%20calls%20of%20a%20leopard%20or%20a%20sambar%20deer%20instead!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJai%20Dhar%20Gupta%20experiences%20this%20every%20day%20at%20his%20biosphere%20in%20Uttarakhand%2C%20nestled%20in%20the%20Shivalik%20foothills%2C%20overlooking%20the%20stunning%20Raghati%20river.%20At%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F337165%2Fstartup-leopard-tech-lab-helps-kerala-forest-department-combat-wildlife-crime%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERajaji%20Raghati%20biosphere%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20all%20you%20need%20to%20do%20is%20sit%20on%20a%20rock%20and%20watch%20as%20leopards%2C%20elephants%2C%20and%20leopards%20pass%20by%2C%20while%20the%20air%20is%20filled%20with%20the%20sounds%20of%20chirping%20birds%20and%20buzzing%20insects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20data-tracker%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3Barticle_name%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3BArticle%20Page%20Ad%20Banner%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Bposition%26quot%3B%3A1%2C%26quot%3Barticle_id%26quot%3B%3A498044%7D%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcampaign.thebetterindia.com%2Ftbi-showcase%2F%5C%22%20data-carousel%3D%5C%22adbanner%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Article%20Ad%20Banner%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fad-banner-1756106894.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESounds%20idyllic%2C%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20it%3F%20This%2032-acre%20biosphere%2C%20located%20within%20Rajaji%20National%20Park%20in%20Uttarakhand%2C%20is%20the%20brainchild%20of%20Jai%2C%20a%2052-year-old%20environmentalist%20and%20entrepreneur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInspired%20by%20the%20mo