lass%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMillets%3A%20Ancient%20grains%20for%20modern%20kids%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20microgreens%20are%20the%20newcomers%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F314758%2Fmothers-start-rigdam-foods-ready-to-eat-millet-snacks-for-children-earn-turnover-in-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emillets%20are%20the%20wise%20elders%3C%2Fa%3E%20making%20a%20comeback.%20For%20centuries%2C%20%3Cem%3Eragi%20laddoos%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Ejowar%20rotis%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Ebajra%20khichdi%20%3C%2Fem%3Efilled%20Indian%20plates.%20Then%2C%20as%20polished%20rice%20and%20packaged%20cereals%20gained%20popularity%2C%20millets%20slipped%20into%20the%20background.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20they%E2%80%99re%20returning%2C%20not%20as%20%E2%80%9Csuperfoods%20of%20the%20West%E2%80%9D%2C%20but%20as%20staples%20with%20deep%20Indian%20roots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20we%20all%20know%2C%20millets%20are%20a%20powerhouse%20of%20complex%20carbohydrates%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sandhya.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20don%E2%80%99t%20just%20give%20energy%2C%20they%20also%20provide%20fibre%2C%20iron%2C%20and%20calcium.%20They%20support%20steady%20growth%2C%20bone%20strength%2C%20and%20even%20cognitive%20development%20in%20children.%20And%20for%20India%2C%20millets%20are%20a%20blessing%20because%20they%20grow%20easily%20in%20our%20soil.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanchita%20emphasises%20that%20the%20approach%20to%20millets%20matters%3A%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20introduce%20them%20in%20a%20child%E2%80%99s%20first%20foods%2C%20say%2C%20%3Cem%3Eragi%20%3C%2Fem%3Eporridge%20at%20seven%20months%2C%20they%20accept%20it%20as%20normal.%20But%20if%20you%20suddenly%20swap%20rice%20for%20jowar%20at%20age%20five%2C%20there%20will%20be%20resistance.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20I%20recommend%20to%20clients%20is%20that%20for%20the%20first%20two%20to%20three%20weeks%2C%20you%20start%20with%20just%20fruits%20and%20vegetables%20to%20let%20your%20child%20ease%20into%20solids.%20Around%20six%20and%20a%20half%20months%2C%20you%20can%20introduce%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F343315%2Fbiggest-millet-exporters-in-india-ra-foods-sisters-priya-akila-gunasekar-run-multi-crore-millet-business%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrains%20like%20%3Cem%3Eragi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20jowar%2C%20quinoa%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20rice%2C%20since%20they%20need%20the%20carbs.%20To%20make%20these%20easier%20to%20digest%2C%20you%20can%20soak%20them%20overnight%20in%20warm%20water%20or%20even%20with%20a%20little%20lemon%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20suggests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanchita%20also%20notes%20that%20millets%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20feel%20%E2%80%9Cboring%E2%80%9D%20or%20traditional.%20%E2%80%9CParents%20can%20make%20millet%20waffles%2C%20millet%20pizza%20bases%2C%20or%20even%20millet-based%20cookies.%20Kids%20respond%20better%20when%20the%20food%20looks%20familiar%20but%20is%20nutritionally%20upgraded.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-instagram%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDK9U1MqNhDE%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDK9U1MqNhDE%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdi