ing%20except%20pasta%20and%20biscuits%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sandhya.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20trick%20is%20persistence%20and%20creativity.%20If%20a%20millet%20pancake%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20work%20one%20day%2C%20try%20millet%20%3Cem%3Eidli%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethe%20next%20%E2%80%94%20or%20millet%20cookies%2C%20chocolates%2C%20even%20burgers%20with%20millet%20patties.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20give%20up%20after%20one%20rejection.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanchita%20adds%20her%20practical%20hacks%3A%20%E2%80%9CIf%20your%20child%20loves%20pasta%2C%20swap%20the%20base%20for%20millet%20pasta%20%E2%80%94%20it%E2%80%99s%20available%20now.%20Or%20make%20the%20sauce%20more%20nutrient-rich%20by%20blending%20in%20spinach%2C%20pumpkin%2C%20or%20microgreens.%20You%20don%E2%80%99t%20always%20have%20to%20reinvent%20meals%2C%20just%20upgrade%20them.%20Take%20the%20foods%20they%20already%20like%20and%20make%20small%20changes.%20For%20example%2C%20add%20a%20pinch%20of%20spirulina%20to%20pancakes%2C%20make%20a%20%3Cem%3Eragi%20%3C%2Fem%3Echocolate%20popsicle%20or%20smoothie%2C%20or%20mix%20a%20spoon%20of%20amaranth%20seeds%20into%20rice.%20It%E2%80%99s%20the%20same%20colour%2C%20so%20they%20won%E2%80%99t%20even%20notice%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20experts%20agree%20that%20a%20fun%20presentation%20matters.%20A%20spinach%20%3Cem%3Edosa%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebecomes%20a%20%E2%80%98Hulk%20dosa%E2%80%99.%20An%20%3Cem%3Eidli%3C%2Fem%3E%20with%20%3Cem%3Echutney%3C%2Fem%3E%20eyes%20transforms%20into%20a%20bunny.%20Bento%20boxes%20%E2%80%94%20those%20colourful%2C%20compartmentalised%20lunch%20kits%20trending%20on%20Instagram%20%E2%80%94%20can%20also%20help%20make%20food%20visually%20exciting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-instagram%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDLALf0oSNdH%2F