.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fonam-1-1757051486.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D496501%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Beyond%20the%20Onam%20%E2%80%98Sadya%E2%80%99%20lies%20a%20world%20of%20vibrant%20traditions%20%E2%80%94%20from%20lively%20dances%20and%20colourful%20masks%20to%20folk%20songs%20and%20thrilling%20boat%20races.%20Together%2C%20these%20rituals%20capture%20the%20true%20spirit%20of%20Kerala%E2%80%99s%20beloved%20festival.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F496501%2Fbeyond-sadya-onam-rituals-folk-songs-tiger-dance-boat-race-kerala-festival%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Growing%20a%20Rangoli%20Garden%20at%20Home%20Teaches%20Kids%20the%20Joy%20of%20Sustainability%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERangoli%20is%20a%20traditional%20art%20form%20where%20vibrant%20patterns%20are%20created%20on%20the%20ground%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F397796%2Fmakar-sankranti-recipes-using-til-cookies-chikki-makhana-barfi-til-papdi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecelebrate%20festivals%20and%20special%20occasions%3C%2Fa%3E.%20More%20than%20just%20decoration%2C%20it%20is%20an%20expression%20of%20beauty%2C%20culture%2C%20and%20creativity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20many%20households%20today%20rely%20on%20store-bought%20powders%20for%20convenience%2C%20there%20is%20a%20growing%20movement%20to%20return%20to%20nature%20by%20cultivating%20a%20rangoli%20garden%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20practical%20approach%20brings%20children%20closer%20to%20age-old%20traditions%20while%20teaching%20them%20about%20sustainability%2C%20gardening%2C%20and%20the%20natural%20sources%20of%20colour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20data-tracker%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3Barticle_name%26quot%3B%